239
00:12:04,612 --> 00:12:07,142
I don't get it.
You worked so hard yesterday.

240
00:12:08,719 --> 00:12:10,145
But then, so did I.

241
00:12:12,582 --> 00:12:14,328
Oh. Now I'm sad again.

242
00:12:14,609 --> 00:12:15,650
Morning, ladies.

243
00:12:15,818 --> 00:12:18,278
Notice anything redder
about me?

244
00:12:19,816 --> 00:12:23,325
I am literally shaking
with jealousy. Get out!

245
00:12:23,493 --> 00:12:26,161
I don't want the coat to see me
like this. No, wait.

246
00:12:27,416 --> 00:12:28,966
Let me touch it.
No.

247
00:12:29,107 --> 00:12:30,165
No. Wait.

248
00:12:32,676 --> 00:12:33,676
Your call.

249
00:12:38,893 --> 00:12:41,256
I've been thinking about
how I behaved last night,

250
00:12:41,381 --> 00:12:44,640
